article.description: — Duke Miles' 20 points helped High Point defeat Mount Olive 122-73 on Sunday.
article.headline: Miles scores 20 as High Point defeats Mount Olive 122-73
article.linkText: Miles scores 20 as High Point defeats Mount Olive 122-73
article.story: AMHERST, Mass. -- — Duke Miles' 20 points helped High Point defeat Mount Olive 122-73 on Sunday. Miles also had six assists for the Panthers (4-3). Kezza Giffa scored 19 points and added six assists. Trae Benham finished 4 of 8 from 3-point range to finish with 12 points. Josiah Watkins finished with 12 points, seven rebounds, six assists and two steals for the Trojans. Trey Nelson added 11 points for Mount Olive. Aaron Murphy also had 10 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
